snippet.title: Chants of Sennaar - Official Behind The Glyphs Trailer | Tribeca Games Spotlight 2023
snippet.description:
Chants of Sennaar is a puzzle adventure game where players will decipher glyphs to unravel the mysteries of forgotten languages. The game takes players on a journey to a foreign realm where five Peoples live divided and reuniting them requires the solution to the puzzles that scatter the world. Chants of Sennaar is launching on September 5 for PlayStation 4, Xbox One, Nintendo Switch, and PC.

#GameTrailers #SummerOfGaming
